---
import GamesLayout from '../../layouts/GamesLayout.astro';
---

<GamesLayout title="My Own Piece of Somewhere" description="My Own Piece of Somewhere — a cozy life sim and city builder by Quiet Atlas. Build a town, then learn to belong to it.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="game-hero">
    <div class="game-hero-visual game-hero-image somewhere-hero-bg">
      <div class="game-hero-overlay"></div>
      <div class="game-hero-content container fade-in">
        <span class="game-hero-label">Cozy Life Sim + City Builder · Belonging</span>
        <h1 class="game-hero-title">My Own Piece of Somewhere</h1>
        <p class="game-hero-tagline">You build a place — then learn to belong to it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section class="game-about container">
    <div class="content-width">
      <div class="game-lead fade-in">
        <p class="lead-text">
          You slowly build a small town inspired by global cultural styles — then live inside it
          in first person. You are not the mayor. You are a resident seeking belonging. No grind.
          No pressure. Only presence.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pull-quote fade-in">
        "No grind. No pressure. Only presence."
      </div>

      <div class="game-details fade-in">
        <h2>Emotional Experience</h2>
        <p>
          Peace and stillness. Belonging and rootedness. Ritual and daily rhythm. Cultural
          immersion. Slow living. This is a long-term vision project — a place to return to,
          not to finish.
        </p>

        <h2>Core Loop</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Zen city planning</strong> — Small beginnings, token-based expansion,
          aesthetic-driven building, cultural district styles. You shape the town at your own pace.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Living inside the town</strong> — Visit shops, walk streets, daily rituals,
          seasonal atmosphere. First-person presence in the world you helped create.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>NPC-driven economy</strong> — Shops operate autonomously. Passive income.
          The player focuses on experience, not grind.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Cultural immersion</strong> — Architecture and lifestyle inspirations from
          around the world. Optional language exposure. Atmosphere over gamification.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="game-features stagger-children">
        <div class="feature-card card">
          <h3>Resident, Not Mayor</h3>
          <p>You're not running the town — you're living in it. Building is the path to belonging.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card card">
          <h3>First-Person Living</h3>
          <p>After building, you walk the streets, visit shops, and breathe the world you made.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card card">
          <h3>No Grind</h3>
          <p>Autonomous economy. Passive income. Your job is to be present, not to optimize.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="signature fade-in">
        <p><strong>Signature identity:</strong> You build a place — then learn to belong to it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Info -->
  <section class="game-info container">
    <div class="info-grid fade-in">
      <div class="info-block">
        <h3>Status</h3>
        <p>Long-term Vision</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-block">
        <h3>Genre</h3>
        <p>Life Sim + City Builder</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-block">
        <h3>Platform</h3>
        <p>TBD</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-block">
        <h3>Engine</h3>
        <p>Godot</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta container">
    <div class="cta-inner fade-in">
      <hr class="ornamental" />
      <p class="cta-text">Somewhere is still on the map. We'll share more as the road becomes clear.</p>
      <a href="https://quietatlas.itch.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-large">Follow on itch.io</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</GamesLayout>

<style>
  .game-hero {
    margin-top: calc(-1 * var(--nav-height));
  }

  .game-hero-visual {
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
  }

  .game-hero-image {
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }

  .somewhere-hero-bg {
    background-image: url('/images/games/somewhere-concept.png');
    background-color: #0a1a0f;
  }

  .game-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(8, 8, 12, 0.3) 0%, rgba(8, 8, 12, 0.9) 100%);
  }

  .game-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .game-hero-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .game-hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .game-hero-tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.35rem);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .game-about {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  }

  .lead-text {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .game-details {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .game-details h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .game-details p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .signature {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
  }

  .signature p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .game-features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .game-features {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .game-info {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .info-block h3 {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .info-block p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .info-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .cta {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
</style>
